Library/

# dev-only vault key — see backend/src/vault/crypto.rs `load_or_create_dev_key`.
# Lives at ~/Library/Application Support/Tersh/.dev-vault-key.b64 at runtime;
# this pattern catches any stray copy that ends up in-tree.
.dev-vault-key.b64

# release
release/
*.dmg
*.app
*.exe
*.AppImage
*.deb
*.rpm
*.msi

# ── leak hardening (audited 2026-05-31; root rules already cover *.pem *.key
# id_rsa*/id_dsa*/id_ecdsa*/id_ed25519* *.p12 *.keystore *.kdbx *.1pux
# wallet.dat secrets.json secret.json .env* *.db *.sqlite* .dev-vault-key.b64) ──

